<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Default Header</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">The standard header for all public-facing pages. Fixed to the top of the viewport so it remains accessible during scroll. The semi-transparent glass pills float above page content without blocking the layout below — this works best when the page hero or background image extends behind the header.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview ds-preview--dark" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden; min-height: 80px; position: relative;">
    <header class="header" style="position: relative; top: auto; left: auto; right: auto;">
      <div class="header__pill header__left">
        <a href="#" class="header__logo" aria-label="Regent's University London">
          <img src="/public/Logo.svg" alt="Regent's University London" width="32" height="32">
        </a>
        <nav class="header__nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
          <a href="#" class="header__nav-link header__nav-link--active">
            Study
            <svg class="header__nav-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">
            International
            <svg class="header__nav-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">
            Why Regent's
            <svg class="header__nav-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="header__pill header__right">
        <a href="#" class="header__apply">Apply now</a>
        <div class="header__pill-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <button class="header__icon-btn" aria-label="Search">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="header__pill-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <button class="header__icon-btn" aria-label="Open navigation menu">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Mobile (≤768px)</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Below 768px the primary nav and Apply now link are hidden. The left pill collapses to the logo only; the right pill retains Search and the hamburger trigger (the divider between Apply now and Search is also hidden). This keeps the header compact at 8px vertical padding while preserving the two essential actions.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview ds-preview--dark" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden; min-height: 64px; position: relative; max-width: 390px;">
    <header class="header" style="position: relative; top: auto; left: auto; right: auto; padding: var(--sp-8) var(--sp-16);">
      <div class="header__pill header__left" style="padding: var(--sp-8);">
        <a href="#" class="header__logo" aria-label="Regent's University London">
          <img src="/public/Logo.svg" alt="Regent's University London" width="32" height="32">
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="header__pill header__right">
        <button class="header__icon-btn" aria-label="Search">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="header__pill-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <button class="header__icon-btn" aria-label="Open navigation menu">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>
</div>

